title: Jazz - Django & Grappelli 1934-49 Complete
description:
Jazz - Django & Grappelli 1934-49 Complete [122 chronological]

I compiled this myself, and so it may be the only such compilation available.
Though Django Reinhardt and Stephane Grappelli are best known for playing together, they both did great jazz separately as well, and other compilations of Django include non-Grappelli.
Django was the first hugely influential jazz figure to emerge from Europe.
